name: Sleen
Lore: 'Slow, omnivorous swamp forager. Eats insects. Seeks damp, dark environments strong with the Force.',
Text: 'Ferocity = destiny - 3. Habitat: planet sites (except Hoth and Tatooine) and Dark Waters. Cumulatively absorbs (temporarily cancels) one [Light Side Force] icon present. Parasite: None.',
